Package com.seailz.discordjv.model.interaction.reply

Interface InteractionReply

All Superinterfaces:
Compilerable
All Known Implementing Classes:
InteractionMessageResponse, InteractionModalResponse
public interface InteractionReply extends Compilerable
Represents a reply to an interaction. This could include things such as a modal, or a message.

This class itself (InteractionReply) is not a functional class and is used to mark interaction replies.

A list of responses can be found here A list of responses supported in Discord.jv can be found in this package.
